in%20July%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bsaved%20by%20God%20to%20make%20America%20great%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20received%20standing%20ovations%20when%20he%20declared%20that%20he%20would%20announce%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20emergency%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20southern%20border%20in%20Mexico%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20energy%20emergency%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20allow%20oil%20extractors%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrill%2C%20baby%20drill%26quot%3B%20-%20issues%20that%20had%20been%20key%20campaign%20pitches%20and%20resonated%20with%20his%20'Make%20America%20Great%20Again'%20(MAGA)%20supporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERattling%20off%20other%20key%20talking%20points%20of%20his%20campaign%2C%20which%20may%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%2C%20the%20President%20said%20his%20administration%20would%20deport%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20and%20millions%26quot%3B%20of%20undocumented%20migrants%2C%20%26quot%3Btariff%20and%20tax%26quot%3B%20foreign%20countries%2C%20%26quot%3Btake%20back%26quot%3B%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20and%20rename%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20positioned%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeacemaker%20and%20unifier%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20to%20some%20Israeli%20hostages%20being%20handed%20back%20by%20Hamas%2C%20and%20said%20he%20would%20lead%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20to%20new%20heights%20-%20including%20by%20sending%20astronauts%20to%20Mars%20-%20and%20make%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bgreater%20than%20ever%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20taking%20oath%20as%20messages%20of%20congratulations%2C%20including%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20poured%20in%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Golden%20age%20of%20America%20begins%20right%20now.%20America%20will%20soon%20be%20greater%2C%20stronger%2C%20and%20far%20more%20exceptional%20than%20ever%20before.%20I%20return%20to%20the%20presidency%20confident%20and%20optimistic%20that%20we%20are%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20thrilling%20new%20era%20of%20national%20success.%20A%20tide%20of%20change%20is%20sweeping%20the%20country.%20Sunlight%20is%20pouring%20over%20the%20entire%20world.%20and%20America%20has%20the%20chance%20to%20seize%20this%20opportunity%20like%20never%20before.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20this%20day%20forward%2C%20our%20country%20will%20flourish%20and%20be%20respected%20again%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20We%20will%20be%20the%20envy%20of%20every%20nation%20and%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20ourselves%20to%20be%20taken%20advantage%20of%20any%20longer.%20During%20every%20single%20day%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20I%20will%20very%20simply%20put%20America%20first.%20Our%20sovereignty%20will%20be%20reclaimed.%20Our%20safety%20will%20be%20restored.%20The%20scales%20of%20justice%20will%20be%20rebalanced...%20And%20our%20top%20priority%20will%20be%20to%20create%20a%20nation%20that%20is%20proud%2C%20prosperous%2C%20and%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20him%2C%20after%20which%20Elon%20Musk%20-%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20-%20publicly%20declared%20that%20he%20was%20endorsing%20the%20Republican%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20wish%20to%20stop%20our%20cause%20have%20tried%20to%20take%20my%20freedom%20and%20indeed%2C%20to%20take%20my%20life.%20Just%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20in%20a%20beautiful%20Pennsylvania%20field%2C%20an%20assassin's%20bullet%20ripped%20through%20my%20ear.%20But%20I%20felt%20then%2C%20and%20believe%20even%20more%20so%20now%2C%20that%20my%20life%20was%20saved%20for%20a%20reason.%20I%20was%20saved%20by%20God%20to%20make%20America%20great%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExecutive%20Orders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20his%20intention%20to%20sign%20a%20raft%20of%20executive%20orders%2C%20which%20carry%20the%20force%20of%20law%20but%20do%20not%20require%20Congressional%20approval%2C%20Trump%20got%20a%20standing%20ovation%20when%20he%20said%20he%20would%20declare%20a%20national%20emergency%20at%20the%20country's%20southern%20border%20with%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20illegal%20entry%20will%20immediately%20be%20halted%20and%20we%20will%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20returning%20millions%20and%20millions%20of%20criminal%20aliens%20back%20to%20the%20places%20from%20which%20they%20came.%20We%20will%20reinstate%20my%20remain-in-Mexico%20policy.%20I%20will%20end%20the%20practice%20of%20catch%20and%20release.%20And%20I%20will%20send%20troops%20to%20the%20southern%20border%20to%20repel%20the%20disastrous%20invasion%20of%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20invoking%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act%20of%201798.%20I%20will%20direct%20our%20government%20to%20use%20the%20full%20and%20immense%20power%20of%20federal%20and%20state%20law%20enforcement%20to%20eliminate%20the%20presence%20of%20all%20foreign%20gangs%20and%20criminal%20networks%20bringing%20devastating%20crime%20to%20US%20soil%2C%20including%20our%20cities%20and%20inner%20cities.%20As%20Commander%20in%20Chief%2C%20I%20have%20no%20higher%20responsibility%20than%20to%20defend%20our%20country%20from%20threats%20and%20invasions%2C%20and%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20am%20going%20to%20do.%20We%20will%20do%20it%20at%20a%20level%20that%20nobody%20has%20ever%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20used%20his%20catchphrase%20of%20%26quot%3Bdrill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20declare%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20energy%20emergency%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inflation%20crisis%20was%20caused%20by%20massive%20overspending%20and%20escalating%20energy%20prices%20and%20that%20is%20why%20today%20I%20will%20also%20declare%20a%20national%20energy%20emergency.%20We%20will%20drill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill.%20America%20will%20be%20a%20manufacturing%20nation%20once%20again%2C%20and%20we%20have%20something%20that%20no%20other%20manufacturing%20nation%20will%20ever%20have%2C%20the%20largest%20amount%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20of%20any%20country%20on%20Earth%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20use%20it...We%20will%20be%20a%20rich%20nation%20again%20and%20it%20is%20that%20liquid%20gold%20under%20our%20feet%20that%20will%20help%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20President%20also%20said%20he%20would%20revoke%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20%26quot%3Bmandate%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Btariff%20and%20tax%26quot%3B%20foreign%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20immediately%20begin%20the%20overhaul%20of%20our%20trade%20system%20to%20protect%20American%20workers%20and%20families.%20Instead%20of%20taxing%20our%20citizens%20to%20enrich%20other%20countries%2C%20we%20will%20tariff%20and%20tax%20foreign%20countries%20to%20enrich%20our%20citizens.%20For%20this%20purpose%2C%20we%20are%20establishing%20the%20External%20Revenue%20Service%20to%20collect%20all%20tariffs%2C%20duties%20and%20revenues.%20It%20will%20be%20massive%20amounts%20of%20money%20pouring%20into%20our%20treasury%20coming%20from%20foreign%20sources.%20The%20American%20Dream%20will%20soon%20be%20back%20and%20thriving%20like%20never%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20on%20to%20other%20pet%20issues%2C%20some%20of%20which%20he%20began%20talking%20about%20after%20winning%20re-election%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20rename%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20and%20take%20back%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20treated%20very%20badly%20from%20this%20foolish%20gift%20that%20should%20have%20never%20been%20made%20and%20Panama's%20promise%20to%20us%20has%20been%20broken.%20The%20purpose%20of%20our%20deal%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20our%20treaty%20have%20been%20totally%20violated.%20American%20ships%20are%20being%20severely%20overcharged%20and%20not%20treated%20fairly%20in%20any%20way%2C%20shape%20or%20form...%20that%20includes%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%20And%2C%20above%20all%2C%20China%20is%20operating%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20and%20we%20didn't%20give%20it%20to%20China.%20We%20gave%20it%20to%20Panama%20and%20we're%20taking%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BCorrupt%20Establishment%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20Biden%20government%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20many%20years%2C%20a%20radical%20and%20corrupt%20establishment%20has%20extracted%20power%20and%20wealth%20from%20our%20citizens%2C%20while%20the%20pillars%20of%20our%20society%20lay%20broken%20and%20seemingly%20in%20complete%20disrepair.%20We%20now%20have%20a%20government%20that%20cannot%20manage%20even%20a%20simple%20crisis%20at%20home%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20stumbling%20into%20a%20continuing%20catalogue%20of%20catastrophic%20events%20abroad.%20It%20fails%20to%20protect%20our%20magnificent%2C%20law-abiding%20American%20citizens%2C%20but%20provides%20sanctuary%20and%20protection%20for%20dangerous%20criminals%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20problems%20under%20the%20previous%20administration%2C%20Trump%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20wildfires%20in%20California%2C%20which%20burned%20through%20large%20swathes%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20where%20we%20are%20watching%20fires%20still%20tragically%20burn%20from%20weeks%20ago%20without%20even%20a%20token%20of%20defence.%20They're%20raging%20through%20the%20houses%20and%20communities%2C%20even%20affecting%20some%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20and%20most%20powerful%20individuals%20in%20our%20country%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20sitting%20here%20right%20now.%20They%20don't%20have%20a%20home%20any%20longer.%20That's%20interesting%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20let%20this%20happen.%20Everyone%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20anything%20about%20it.%20That's%20going%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20said%20the%20public%20health%20system%20in%20the%20US%20does%20not%20deliver%20in%20times%20of%20disaster%20despite%20more%20money%20being%20spent%20on%20it%20than%20any%20country%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20have%20an%20education%20system%20that%20teaches%20our%20children%20to%20be%20ashamed%20of%20themselves%2C%20in%20many%20cases%20to%20hate%20our%20country%20despite%20the%20love%20that%20we%20try%20so%20desperately%20to%20provide%20to%20them.%20All%20of%20this%20will%20change%20starting%20today%2C%20and%20it%20will%20change%20very%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737401400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F7n9sfb4o_trump-swearing-_625x300_20_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgolden-age-of-america-begins-right-now-trump-takes-oath-as-us-president-7519656%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20oath%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20age%26quot%3B%20of%20America%20has%20begun%20and%20the%20country%20will%20be%20the%20envy%20of%20every%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22United%20States%3A%20Hyderabad%20youth%20shot%20dead%20in%20likely%20carjacking%20in%20DC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737401385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117407221%2Cimgsize-110284.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fhyd-youth-shot-dead-in-carjacking-in-dc%2Farticleshow%2F117407222.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2026-year-old%20MBA%20graduate%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20working%20part-time%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20was%20fatal