ring%20boom%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe2.org%2Freports%2Fclean-economy-works-two-year-review-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredominantly%20in%20Republican%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20new%20factories%20are%20churning%20out%20solar%20panels%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20batteries%20that%20can%20reduce%20planet-warming%20emissions%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20fossil%20fuel%20production%2C%20administration%20officials%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20the%20orders%20will%20aim%20to%20boost%20supplies%20of%20non-fuel%20minerals%20and%20that%20the%20actions%20will%20increase%20consumer%20choice%20for%20a%20range%20of%20manufactured%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20about%2024%25%20of%20oil%20and%2011%25%20of%20natural%20gas%20are%20produced%20on%20federal%20lands%20and%20waters%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.api.org%2Fnews-policy-and-issues%2Fexploration-and-production%2Fdrilling-down-on-the-federal-leasing-facts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustry%20estimates.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20vast%20majority%20comes%20from%20private%20land%20owned%20by%20individuals%20and%20companies.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-executive-orders-oil-gas-energy-electric-vehicles-epa-interior-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20limited%20drilling%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20federal%20areas%20like%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20and%20Alaska%20and%20paused%20new%20permits%20for%20terminals%20to%20export%20gas%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroups%20representing%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20industry%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.api.org%2Fnews-policy-and-issues%2Fnews%2F2024%2F11%2F12%2Fapi-releases-new-policy-roadmap-for-incoming-administration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20American%20Petroleum%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20those%20moves%20cost%20jobs%20at%20home%20