0company%20will%20change%2C%20with%20Sacheti%20and%20Plutus%20Wealth%20Management%20becoming%20the%20main%20promoters%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%202%20Genders%2C%20Emergency%20At%20Mexico%20Border%3A%20Orders%20Trump%20Will%20Sign%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20was%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20historic%20second%20term%20as%20US%20president%20on%20Monday%2C%20capping%20his%20extraordinary%20return.%20In%20his%20first%20speech%20after%20the%20oath%2C%20he%20mentioned%20a%20blitz%20of%20immediate%20orders%20on%20immigration%C2%A0gender%20identity%20policies%2C%20immigration%2C%20climate%20and%20energy%20policy%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0These%20executive%20orders%20are%20mainly%20aimed%20at%20fulfilling%20his%20poll%20promises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20declare%20a%20national%20emergency%20at%20our%20southern%20border%26quot%3B%20with%20Mexico%2C%20Trump%20said%20to%20loud%20cheers%20from%20supporters%20inside%20the%20ornate%20Rotunda%20hall%2C%20vowing%20to%20deport%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20and%20millions%26quot%3B%20of%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20an%20incoming%20White%20House%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20declare%20a%20national%20emergency%20at%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20official.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Executive%20Order%20directs%20the%20military%20to%20prioritise%20our%20borders%20and%20territorial%20integrity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20he%20will%20declare%20a%20national%20energy%20emergency%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20US%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%20and%20lowering%20costs%20for%20US%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inflation%20crisis%20was%20caused%20by%20massive%20over-spending%20and%20escalating%20energy%20prices%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20today%20I%20will%20also%20declare%20a%20national%20energy%20emergency%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Trump%C2%A0said%20in%20the%20US%20Capitol.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20drill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20said%20that%20his%20government's%20official%20policy%20would%20only%20recognise%20two%20genders.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20will%20also%20end%20the%20government%20policy%20of%20trying%20to%20socially%20engineer%20race%20and%20gender%20into%20every%20aspect%20of%20public%20and%20private%20life...%20As%20of%20today%2C%20it%20will%20henceforth%20be%20the%20official%20policy%20of%20the%20United%20States%20government%20that%20there%20are%20only%20two%20genders%2C%20male%20and%20female.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20executive%20orders%20will%20also%20target%20diversity%20programs%2C%20moving%20swiftly%20to%20deliver%20on%20divisive%20campaign%20promises%20to%20dismantle%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Treasury%20--%20this%20is%20a%20little%20a%20while%20ago%20now%20--%20included%20diversity%20training%20that%20said%20all%20white%20people%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20woke%20they%20are%2C%20contribute%20to%20racism.%20So%20this%20type%20of%20funding%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20end%20at%20these%20(diversity)%20programs.%20We're%20going%20to%20end%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20Trump%20criticised%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20policies%20in%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20saying%20they%20discriminated%20against%20white%20people%20-%20men%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20orders%20will%20intend%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%20for%20US-born%20children%20whose%20parents%20lack%20legal%20immigration%20status.%20%26quot%3BThe%20federal%20government%20will%20not%20recognize%20automatic%20birthright%20citizenship%20for%20children%20of%20illegal%20aliens%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20to%20the%20US%20Constitution%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20going%20to%20enhance%20vetting%20and%20screening%20of%20illegal%20aliens%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20executive%20order%20is%20an%20order%20issued%20unilaterally%20by%20the%20president%20who%20carries%20the%20force%20of%20law.%20Unlike%20legislation%2C%20executive%20orders%20do%20not%20require%20Congressional%20approval.%20Though%20Congress%20cannot%20overturn%20them%2C%20they%20can%20be%20challenged%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Stephen%20Miller%2C%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20Trump%2C%20the%20orders%20will%20be%20around%20these%20five%20points%20-%20sealing%20the%20Southern%20border%2C%20mass%20deportation%2C%20preventing%20transgender%20people%20from%20women's%20sports%2C%20removing%20restrictions%20on%20energy%20exploration%20and%20improving%20government%20efficiency.%20Among%20his%20executive%20orders%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20pardoning%20his%20supporters%20who%20were%20arrested%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20for%20their%20role%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20roll%20back%20some%20of%20the%20orders%20and%20actions%20of%20the%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Prominent%20among%20them%20include%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Agreement%2C%20lifting%20restrictions%20on%20fossil%20fuel%20production%20and%20expanding%20domestic%20oil%20drilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20made%20history%20by%20replacing%20Biden%20as%20the%20oldest%20president%20to%20be%20sworn%20in.%20He%20is%20also%20just%20the%20second%20president%20in%20US%20history%20to%20return%20to%20power%20after%20being%20voted%20out%2C%20after%20Grover%20Cleveland%20in%201893.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737396180000%2C%22visu