e%20similar%20pardons%20to%20members%20and%20staff%20of%20the%20US%20House%20committee%20that%20investigated%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%20attack%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%20by%20Donald%20Trump's%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20commuted%20to%20home%20confinement%20the%20life%20sentence%20of%20Native%20American%20activist%20Leonard%20Peltier%2C%2080%2C%20who%20has%20been%20imprisoned%20for%20nearly%2050%20years%20for%20the%201975%20murders%20of%20two%20FBI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20and%20I%20am%20optimistic%20that%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20legal%20institutions%20will%20ultimately%20prevail%20over%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20announcing%20the%20pardons%20of%20Fauci%2C%20Milley%20and%20the%20members%20of%20the%20January%206%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20these%20are%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20and%20I%20cannot%20in%20good%20conscience%20do%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20public%20servants%20have%20served%20our%20nation%20with%20honor%20and%20distinction%20and%20do%20not%20deserve%20to%20be%20the%20targets%20of%20unjustified%20and%20politically%20motivated%20prosecutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20promised%20%26quot%3Bretribution%26quot%3B%20against%20his%20political%20opponents%20and%20threatened%20some%20with%20criminal%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFauci%2C%20who%20led%20the%20country's%20fight%20against%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20has%20become%20a%20hated%20figure%20for%20many%20on%20the%20right%2C%20including%20Trump%20ally%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20called%20for%20the%20scientist%20to%20be%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20enraged%20after%20Milley%2C%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%2C%20told%20journalist%20Bob%20Woodward%20that%20the%20Republican%20was%20%26quot%3Bfascist%20to%20the%20core%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilley%20also%20revealed%20he%20had%20secretly%20called%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20after%20the%20Capitol%20attack%20to%20reassure%20Beijing%20that%20the%20United%20States%20remained%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20attack%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20subsequently%20wrote%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20network%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20times%20gone%20by%2C%20the%20punishment%20would%20have%20been%20DEATH!%26quot%3B%20for%20Milley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilley%20thanked%20Biden%20for%20his%20executive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20spend%20whatever%20remaining%20time%20the%20Lord%20grants%20me%20fighting%20those%20who%20unjustly%20might%20seek%20retribution%20for%20perceived%20slights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Committed%20no%20crime'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFauci%20also%20thanked%20Biden%20for%20the%20pardon%2C%20according%20to%20US%20media%20reports%2C%20but%20stressed%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20committed%20no%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20minutes%20before%20Trump%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20president%2C%20Biden%20announced%20he%20was%20issuing%20pardons%20to%20his%20brother%20James%20Biden%2C%20James's%20wife%20Sara%20Jones%20Biden%2C%20his%20sister%20Valerie%20Biden%20Owens%2C%20Valerie's%20husband%20John%20Owens%2C%20and%20his%20brother%20Francis%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20family%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20unrelenting%20attacks%20and%20threats%2C%20motivated%20solely%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20hurt%20me%20--%20the%20worst%20kind%20of%20partisan%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20I%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20these%20attacks%20will%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20January%206%20committee%20receiving%20pardons%20i