2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjeff-bezos-fiancee-lauren-sanchez-slammed-for-inappropriate-dress-show-some-respect%2Famp_articleshow%2F117404162.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjeff-bezos-fiancee-lauren-sanchez-slammed-for-inappropriate-dress-show-some-respect%2Famp_articleshow%2F117404162.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Bets%20Satellite%20Spectrum%20Policy%20Can%20Attract%20Many%20Companies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20decision%20to%20allocate%20satellite%20spectrum%2C%20rather%20than%20auction%20it%2C%20will%20give%20consumers%20more%20choice%2C%20the%20telecoms%20minister%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20playing%20down%20concern%20by%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Jio%20that%20it%20could%20lose%20out%20to%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20has%20long%20wanted%20to%20launch%20in%20India%20and%20has%20in%20recent%20months%20clashed%20with%20billionaire%20Ambani's%20company%20over%20how%20the%20country%20should%20grant%20spectrum%20for%20satellite%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20had%20urged%20an%20auction%20but%20the%20Indian%20government%20sided%20with%20Musk%20who%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20allocated%20administratively%2C%20in%20line%20with%20global%20trends.%20Analysts%20say%20an%20auction%2C%20requiring%20much%20more%20investment%2C%20would%20likely%20deter%20foreign%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbani%20said%20he%20wanted%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20and%20has%20been%20worried%20that%20his%20telecom%20company%2C%20which%20spent%20%2419%20billion%20in%20airwave%20auctions%2C%20now%20risks%20losing%20broadband%20customers%20to%20Starlink%20and%20potentially%20even%20data%20and%20voice%20clients%20later%20as%20technology%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20job%20as%20telecoms%20minister%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20have%20as%20many%20choices%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20told%20Reuters%20during%20an%20interview%20at%20his%20ministry's%20office%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20was%20merit%20in%20Reliance's%20concerns%2C%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20any%20company%3A%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20is%20never%20constant%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20companies%20need%20to%20keep%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScindia%20noted%20that%20current%20satellite%20technology%20for%20communications%20requires%20devices%20to%20have%20the%20sky%20in%20their%20sight%2C%20and%20smartphones%20cannot%20use%20that%20technology%20for%20indoor%20services%20that%20are%20provided%20by%20terrestrial%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20minute%20you%20come%20into%20this%20building%2C%20you're%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20telecom%20markets%20with%20942%20million%20users%20and%20stiff%20competition%20among%20Reliance%20and%20rivals%20Bharti%20Airtel%20and%20Vodafone%20Idea.%20Data%20prices%20are%20among%20the%20cheapest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20internet%20connectivity%20has%20risen%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeloitte%20predicts%20India's%20satellite%20broadband%20service%20market%20will%20be%20worth%20%241.9%20billion%20by%202030%2C%20making%20it%20lucrative%20for%20players%20like%20Starlink%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Ambani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScindia%20said%20Starlink%20and%20Amazon%20Kuiper's%20applications%20for%20a%20licence%20to%20launch%20satellite%20broadband%20services%20in%20the%20country%20were%20still%20under%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVODAFONE%20IDEA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20disrupting%20markets.%20In%20Kenya%2C%20he%20priced%20Starlink%20at%20%2410%20per%20month%2C%20versus%20%24120%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20prompting%20a%20complaint%20by%20Kenya's%20Safaricom%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20aviation%20minister%2C%20Scindia%20is%20also%20overseeing%20many%20more%20telecom%20initiatives%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20government%20owns%20a%20stake%20in%20Vodafone%20Idea%2C%20and%20the%20company%20in%20November%20disclosed%20it%20still%20had%20around%20%2424%20billion%20in%20dues%20owed%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScindia%20repeatedly%20declined%20to%20answer%20in%20the%20interview%20if%20there%20were%20any%20plans%20for%20relief%20on%20the%20outstanding%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%2C%20however%2C%20working%20towards%20reviving%20state-run%20telecom%20player%2C%20Bharat%20Sanchar%20Nigam%20Limited%20(BSNL)%2C%20which%20lost%20market%20share%20amid%20fierce%20competition%20over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBSNL%20has%2099%20million%20users%20but%20is%20being%20supported%20with%20expanded%20offerings%20of%204G%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737390960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Foe1nu6fo_-jyotiraditya-scindia_625x300_16_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-elon-musk-mukesh-ambani-tussle-india-bets-satellite-spectrum-policy-can-attract-many-companies-jyotiraditya-scindia-7519382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20decision%20to%20allocate%20satellite%20spectrum%2C%20rather%20than%20auction%20it%2C%20will%20give%20consumers%20more%20choice%2C%20the%20telecoms%20minister%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20playing%20down%20concern%20by%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Jio%20that%20it%20could%20lose%20out%20to%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-elon-musk-mukesh-ambani-tussle-india-bets-satellite-spectrum-policy-can-attract-many-companies-jyotiraditya-sc