-trump-elon-musk-climate-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtests%20against%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20the%20wealthy%20heiress%20of%20a%20German%20business%20empire%20among%20those%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20and%20most%20powerful%20people%20in%20the%20world%20gathered%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20hundreds%20of%20protesters%20blocked%20traffic%2C%20while%20others%20marched%2C%20holding%20signs%20with%20messages%20like%20%26quot%3BEconomy%20for%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTax%20the%20rich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheiress-is-seeking-50-strangers-help-give-away-27m-inheritance-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarlene%20Engelhorn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20inherited%20a%20fortune%20as%20the%20descendant%20of%20a%2019th-century%20German%20industrialist%2C%20was%20among%20those%20marching%20through%20Davos%2C%20calling%20for%20higher%20taxation%20on%20the%20superrich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Engelhorn%20said%20that%20Davos%20sees%20billionaires%20and%20entrepreneurs%20who%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20there%20talking%20to%20world%20leaders%2C%20while%20the%20people%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20going%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20decisions%26quot%3B%20are%20left%20out%20of%20the%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rich%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Balready%20hold%20too%20much%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20we%20are%20facing%20here%20is%20that%20this%20is%20called%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20but%20they%20hide%20away%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%2C%20protected%20by%20the%20military%20and%20the%20police%2C%20in%20order%20to%20talk%20about%20things%20where%20no%20decisions%20are%20being%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngelhorn's%20ancestor%20founded%20BASF%2C%20which%20would%20become%20the%20world's%20largest%20chemical%20producer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20received%20an%20inheritance%20of%20about%20%2427%20million%20after%20her%20grandmother%2C%20Traudl%20Engelhorn-Vechiatto%2C%20died%20in%20September%202022.%20According%20to%20Forbes%2C%20Engelhorn-Vechiatto's%20net%20worth%20was%20%244.2%20billion%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Engelhorn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheiress-asked-strangers-how-to-spend-27m-inheritance-they-decided-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20redistribute%20her%20inheritance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sending%20out%20invitations%20to%20randomly%20selected%20Austrians%20to%20help%20her%20choose%20how%20best%20to%20share%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifty%20people%20were%20chosen%20to%20decide%20how%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20money%20would%20be%20spent%2C%20through%20an%20initiative%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BGood%20Council%20for%20Redistribution%26quot%3B%20(Guter%20Rat%20f%C3%BCr%20R%C3%BCckverteilung%20in%20German).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20the%20group%20decided%20to%20distribute%20roughly%20%2427%20million%20to%2077%20charitable%20initiatives%2C%20including%20several%20women's%20shelter%20associations%2C%20children's%20charities%2C%20and%20climate%20crisis%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20sum%2C%20of%20about%20%241.75%20million%2C%20went%20to%20an%20environmental%20group.%20Other%20beneficiaries%20included%20the%20World%20Inequality%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngelhorn%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20advocate%20for%20people%20like%20her%20to%20be%20taxed%20more%20heavily.%20She%20had%20previously%20called%20on%20Austria%20to%20tax%2090%25%20of%20her%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngelhorn%20also%20took%20part%20in%20protests%20in%20Davos%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20worked%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Fm-le-mag%2Farticle%2F2022%2F11%2F10%2Fmarlene-