r%20RG%20Kar%20Convict%2C%20To%20Go%20To%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExpressing%20her%20disappointment%20that%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20the%20man%20convicted%20of%20raping%20and%20murdering%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20did%20not%20get%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20her%20government%20will%20approach%20the%20High%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20a%20Kolkata%20court%20sentenced%20Roy%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20till%20death%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20-%20whose%20government%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20its%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bmishandling%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20case%20and%20faced%20widespread%20protests%2C%20including%20from%20junior%20doctors%20-%20said%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20would%20have%20ensured%20death%20penalty%20for%20him%2C%20but%20the%20investigation%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20the%20force%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20demanded%20death%20penalty%20from%20Day%201.%20We%20demand%20it%20now%20too.%20But%20it's%20the%20court's%20order.%20I%20can%20share%20my%20party's%20opinion...%20we%20ensured%20death%20penalty%20in%20three%20cases%20within%2060%20days.%20If%20the%20case%20stayed%20with%20us%2C%20we%20would%20have%20ensured%20death%20penalty%20long%20back.%20I%20am%20not%20satisfied...%20Had%20it%20been%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20at%20least%20my%20heart%20would%20have%20been%20somewhat%20at%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bshock%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20judgment%20held%20that%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20did%20not%20fall%20in%20the%20category%20of%20%26quot%3Brarest%20of%20rare%20cases%26quot%3B.%20Asserting%20that%20the%20case%20warrants%20capital%20punishment%2C%20she%20said%20her%20government%20would%20%26quot%3Bplead%26quot%3B%20for%20it%20at%20the%20High%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20convinced%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20rarest%20of%20rare%20case%20which%20demands%20capital%20punishment.%20How%20could%20the%20judgement%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20rarest%20of%20rare%20case%3F!%20%C2%A0We%20want%20and%20insist%20upon%20death%20penalty%20in%20this%20most%20sinister%20and%20sensitive%20case.Recently%2C%20in%20last%203%2F4%20months%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20ensure%20capital%2F%20maximum%20punishment%20for%20convicts%20in%20such%20crimes.%20Then%2C%20why%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20has%20capital%20punishment%20not%20been%20awarded%3F%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20R.G.%20Kar%20junior%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%2C%20I%20am%20really%20shocked%20to%20see%20that%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20Court%20today%20finds%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20Rarest%20of%20Rare%20case!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20convinced%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20rarest%20of%20rare%20case%20which%20demands%20capital%20punishment.%20How%20could%20the%20judgement%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(%40MamataOfficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMamataOfficial%2Fstatus%2F1881344768178848039%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2020%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20a%20heinous%20crime%20that%20warrants%20capital%20punishment.%20We%20will%20plead%20for%20capital%20punishment%20of%20the%20convict%20at%20the%20High%20Court%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737388980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fduniggqo_mamata-banerjee_625x300_06_January_2