recast%20of%20severe%20cold%20weather%20in%20the%20nation's%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20EVENTS%20ARE%20EXPECTED%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20will%20take%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20and%20deliver%20his%20inaugural%20address%20inside%20the%20US%C2%A0%20Capitol%2C%20instead%20of%20outdoors%20in%20front%20of%20the%20building%2C%20as%20initially%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20inaugural%20parade%2C%20which%20was%20set%20to%20include%20marching%20bands%20and%20other%20groups%20proceeding%20down%20Pennsylvania%20Avenue%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20has%20been%20moved%20to%20the%20Capital%20One%20Arena%2C%20a%20professional%20basketball%20and%20hockey%20venue%20in%20downtown%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20held%20a%20campaign-style%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%20Victory%20Rally%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20arena%20on%20Sunday%2C%20putting%20the%20sometimes-maligned%20stadium%20at%20the%20center%20of%20events%20for%20two%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20CAPITAL%20ONE%20ARENA%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arena%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Washington%20Wizards%20NBA%20basketball%20team%20and%20the%20National%20Hockey%20League's%20Washington%20Capitals%20team.%20Built%20in%201997%2C%20it%20is%20located%20near%20the%20city's%20small%20Chinatown%20area%2C%20roughly%20equidistant%20from%20the%20Capitol%20building%20and%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stadium%20also%20hosts%20concerts%20and%20events%20like%20the%20Monster%20Jam%20monster%20truck%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20OWNS%20CAPITAL%20ONE%20ARENA%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arena%20was%20owned%20for%2014%20years%20by%20sports%20mogul%20Ted%20Leonsis%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Monumental%20Sports%20and%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20Wizards%20and%20Capitals.%20The%20District%20of%20Columbia%20bought%20the%20arena%20for%20%2488%20million%20last%20year%2C%20after%20Leonsis%20planned%20to%20relocate%20the%20teams%20across%20the%20Potomac%20River%20to%20an%20arena%20in%20Virginia%20that%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20relocation%20plan%20fell%20apart%2C%20Mayor%20Muriel%20Bowser%20and%20the%20district%20stepped%20in%20to%20keep%20the%20teams%20playing%20in%20D.C.%20The%20district%20is%20leasing%20the%20arena%20back%20to%20MSE%20and%20both%20are%20contributing%20towards%20a%20three-year%2C%20%24800%20million%20redevelopment%20project%20to%20modernize%20the%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeonsis%20also%20owns%20a%20stake%20in%20aXiomatic%2C%20which%20has%20a%20controlling%20interest%20in%20Team%20Liquid%2C%20a%20global%20esports%20powerhouse%20with%20professional%20teams%20in%2014%20games.He%20has%20donated%20in%20the%20past%20to%20both%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20SEATING%20IN%20ARENA%20LIKE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arena%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20hold%20around%2020%2C000%20people%20-%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20approximately%20220%2C000%20ticketed%20guests%20who%20had%20been%20due%20to%20watch%20from%20the%20US%20Capitol%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20WILL%20THE%20TRUMP%20PARADE%20LOOK%20LIKE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20how%20the%20parade%20will%20be%20organized%20inside%20the%20sports%20venue%2C%20but%20Trump%20has%20said%20supporters%20will%20be%20able%20to%20view%20his%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20on%20screens%20inside%20the%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday%20morning%2C%20a%20desk%20was%20sent%20up%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20arena%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20spot%20for%20Trump%20to%20sign%20executive%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737388560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt