placing%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20the%20oldest%20President%20the%20US%20has%20ever%20had.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20new%20era%20dawns%20upon%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20country%20has%20plunged%20into%20a%20deep%20freeze%2C%20forcing%20a%20triumphant%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration%20to%20be%20moved%20indoors%20-%20dampening%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20upbeat%2078-year-old%20and%20his%20passionate%20supporters.%20The%20weather%20forecast%20has%20predicted%20the%20coldest%20inauguration%20day%20in%2040%20years.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20oath%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20magnificent%20US%20Capitol%20in%20front%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20supporters%20assembled%20at%20the%20sprawling%20lawns%20of%20the%20National%20Mall%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20deputy%20JD%20Vance%20will%20take%20oath%20inside%20-%20under%20the%20domed%20Rotunda%20of%20the%20US%20Capitol%2C%20as%20Ronald%20Reagan%20had%20done%20in%201985.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump's%20team%20has%20declared%20that%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20President%20Trump%20places%20his%20hand%20on%20the%20Bible%20and%20swears%20the%20Oath%20to%20the%20United%20States%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Golden%20Age%20of%20America%20will%20begin.%26quot%3B%20However%20millions%20of%20Americans%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20of%20their%20country%2C%20its%20democracy%2C%20pluralism%2C%20and%20economy%2C%20fearing%20the%20consequences%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20dark%20and%20regressive%20promises%20-%20like%20vows%20of%20retribution%20against%20his%20political%20opponents%20and%20journalists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%20said%20he%20will%20take%20immediate%20action%20by%20signing%20a%20record%20number%20of%20executive%20orders%20ushering%20in%20sweeping%20changes%20and%20reversing%20much%20of%20what%20his%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20done.%20This%20he%20says%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bneed%20of%20the%20hour%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump%20returns%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20more%20powerful%20than%20ever%2C%20capping%20a%20journey%20that%20saw%20him%20defy%20two%20assassination%20attempts%20and%20a%20criminal%20conviction%20to%20win%20the%20election%20in%20historic%20fashion%2C%20including%20winning%20every%20single%20swing%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20His%20Republican%20party%20has%20returned%20to%20power%20with%20a%20majority%20in%20both%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Senate%2C%20giving%20President%20Trump%20unhindered%20power%20to%20push%20through%20any%20and%20all%20agendas%20that%20he%20may%20feel%20necessary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReports%20suggest%20that%20President%20Trump's%20immediate%20move%2C%20in%20the%20first%20few%20hours%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20will%20be%20to%20sign%20a%20staggering%20over-100%20executive%20orders%20-%20including%20immediate%20tariff%20implementation%2C%20stringent%20curbs%20on%20immigration%2C%20mass%20deportation%20of%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20a%20national%20emergency%20on%20the%20southern%20US%20border%20with%20Mexico%2C%20ending%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20pardon%20to%20all%202021%20US%20Capitol%20rioters%2C%20ban%20on%20transgender%20athletes%20from%20women's%20sports%2C%20ending%20all%20gender-affirming%20care%20practices%2C%20and%20undoing%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20directives%20on%20diversity%20and%20oil%20drilling%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump's%20return%20as%20President%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20180-degree%20shift%20in%20the%20tech%20industry's%20policies%20in%20terms%20of%20fact%20checks%2C%20inclusiveness%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20social%20sensitivity%20-%20things%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20misinformation%2C%20fake%20news%2C%20divisiveness%2C%20polarisation%2C%20bullying%2C%20and%20targeting%20of%20minorities.%20Big%20tech%20has%20adopted%20Donald%20Trump's%20outlook%2C%20and%20three%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20men%20-%20all%20tech%20tycoons%20-%20X%20and%20SpaceX%20chief%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Amazon%20boss%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20and%20Meta%20(Instagram%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Threads%2C%20WhatsApp)%20chief%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20will%20be%20seen%20alongside%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20inauguration.%20Besides%20them%2C%20the%20list%20of%20tech%20CEOs%20attending%20Trump's%20inauguration%20is%20a%20veritable%20who's%20who%20of%20industry%20giants%2C%20including%20ChatGPT-maker%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20Alphabet%20and%20Google's%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20Microsoft's%20Satya%20Nadella%2C%20Apple's%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20and%20TikTok%20CEO%20Shou%20Chew.%20These%20leaders%20are%20eager%20to%20establish%20a%20positive%20relationship%20with%20the%20incoming%20administration%2C%20particularly%20given%20the%20regulatory%20challenges%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20brings%20a%20heightened%20sense%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20preparing%20for%20the%20unexpected%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20trade%20practices%20and%20geopolitics.%20For%20the%20Americas%2C%20there%20is%20a%20great%20degree%20of%20concern%20over%20Trump's%20open%20threats%20to%20Greenland%2C%20Panama%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Canada.%20There%20is%20worry%20in%20Ukraine%20too%2C%20with%20Trump%20calling%20for%20a%20rethink%20of%20US%20aid%20to%20the%20war-torn%20country%2C%20without%20which%20its%20resistance%20to%20Russia's%20might%20will%20be%20severely%20compromised.%20Promising%20sweeping%20changes%20to%20its%20Middle%20East%20policy%20and%20its%20funding%20of%20NATO%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20sure%20to%20rattle%20the%20global%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEurope%20faces%20a%20huge%20risk%20of%20being%20dominated%2C%20crushed%20and%20marginalised%20if%20they%20do%20nothing%20to%20counter%20the%20policies%20of%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20French%20prime%20minister%20Francois%20Bayrou%20has%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%2C%20with%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20President%2C%20has%20decided%20on%20a%20politics%20that%20is%20incredibly%20dominating%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20French%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20(European%20countries)%20do%20nothing%20then%20our%20fate%20will%20be%20simple.%20We%20will%20be%20dominated%2C%20we%20will%20be%20crushed%2C%20we%20will%20be%20marginalised.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20us%2C%20French%20and%20Europeans%2C%20as%20it%20is%20impossible%20without%20Europe.%26quot%3B%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20had%20even%20before%20Trump's%20election%20for%20a%20second%20term%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20Europe%20gaining%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B%20by%20limiting%20its%20dependence%20on%20the%20United%20States%2C%20particularly%20in%20defence.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20markets%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20optimistic%20about%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%2C%20and%20his%20policies%20on%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20especially%20drilling%20for%20oil%2C%20has%20sent%20the%20US%20and%20global%20markets%20on%20an%20upward%20spiral.%20The%20US%20Dollar%20has%20strengthened%20too%2C%20as%20has%20cryptocurrencies.%20Bitcoin%20hit%20a%20record%20high%20above%20%24109%2C000%20today%20as%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20signalled%20plans%20to%20deregulate%20the%20cryptocurrency%20sector%2C%20prepares%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20US%20President.%20Bitcoin%20surged%20to%20an%20all-time%20peak%20of%20%24109%2C241%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20inauguration%20ceremony%2C%20before%20falling%20back%20to%20around%20%24107%2C500.%20The%20world's%20biggest%20cryptocurrency%20has%20soared%20since%20Trump%20won%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20November%2C%20with%20bitcoin%20surpassing%20%24100%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737383940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2For1krfkg_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_06_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-returns-as-47th-potus-the-history-and-legacy-in-10-points-7518335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20returns%20as%20US%20President%20for%20a%20second%20term%20today%20-%20a%20historic%20one%20on%20several%20counts.%20His%20inauguration%20or%20oath%20ceremony%20at%20the%20US%20Capitol%20will%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%20usher%20in%20a%20new%20era%20-%20whether%20for%20better%20or%20worse%20-%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-returns-as-47th-potus-the-history-and-legacy-in-10-points-7518335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20Davos%2C%20Godrej%20Agrovet%20Chief%20Explains%20AI's%20Critical%20Role%20In%20Food%20Sector%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20big%20themes%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20has%20been%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20food%20and%20agriculture%20is%20something%20that's%20absolutely%20critical.%20Nadir%20Godrej%2C%20Chairperson%20of%20Godrej%20Agrovet%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20at%20Davos%20said%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20a%20big%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20food%20sector%2C%20and%20Godrej%20Agrovet%20is%20using%20AI%20in%20several%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20crop-protection%20business%20where%20we%20produce%20chemicals%20that%20help%20to%20protect%20crops.%20We%20use%20photographs%20to%20find%20crop%20diseases.%20AI%20studies%20the%20photographs%20of%20the%20crops%20and%20determines%20what%20kind%20of%20disease%20it%20is%2C%20and%20that%20is%20very%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Godrej%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20an%20example%20of%20how%20large%20oil%20palm%20plantations%20owned%20by%20smallholders%2C%20who%20don't%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20manage%20the%20plantations%2C%20benefit%20from%20the%20use%20of%20IA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20oil%20palm%20business%2C%20we%20take%20satellite%20photographs%20of%20all%20our%20oil%20palm%20plantations%20which%20are%20owned%20by%20smallholders...%20Once%20we%20see%20the%20photographs%2C%20we%20can%20give%20them%20(smallholders)%20advice%2C%20we%20can%20tell%20them%20what%20kind%20of%20fertilizer%20to%20use%2C%20we%20also%20do%20soil%20testing%2C%20all%20that%20gets%20analysed%2C%20and%20wherever%20possible%2C%20we%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20give%20them%20the%20right%20advice%20to%20improve%20their%20yields%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20oil%20they%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20diversified%20agri-business%20major%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20AI%20helps%20reduce%20inputs%20such%20as%20fertilizers%20and%20costs.%20But%20how%20exactly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20know%20the%20exact%20conditions%20of%20the%20crop%2C%20you%20don't%20overuse%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20overusing%20fertilisers%20causes%20pollution%20and%20damages%20the%20soil%2C%20but%20if%20you%20use%20the%20right%20amount%2C%20it's%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Godrej%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20collaborate%20with%20AI%20firms%20around%20the%20world%2C%20though%20Godrej%20Agrovet%20also%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20AI%20professionals%20on%20its%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20areas%20where%20the%20company%20uses%20AI%20are%20in%20its%20food%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20To%20manage%20stores%2C%20we%20see%20what%20is%20the%20shelf%20space-share%20we%20have%20by%20taking%20photographs%20of%20the%20stores%2C%20which%20all%20get%20analysed%20by%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20all%20our%20sales%20staff%20very%20productive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Godrej%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Trump%20Presidency%20And%20Tariffs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Godrej%20agreed%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20tariffs%20is%20critical%2C%20and%20obviously%20critical%20to%20agriculture%20as%20well.%20With%20Donald%20Trump%202.0%20here%20and%20speculation%20of%20tariff%20wars%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20Mr%20Godrej%20said%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20Indian%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20On%20some%20items%20we%20have%20high%20tariffs.%20It%20would%20be%20good%20for%20us%20to%20proactively%20reduce%20some%20of%20those%20tariffs%3B%20we%20no%20longer%20need%20such%20high%20tariffs%20for%20protection%20of%20our%20industries%2C%20and%20already%20many%20people%20are%20manufacturing%2C%20the%20foreign%20companies%20who%20are%20importing%20those%20products%20are%20already%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%20so%20by%20reducing%20some%20of%20these%20tariffs%2C%20we%20can%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20are%20not%20hit%20by%20high%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Godrej%20said%2C%20adding%20if%20China%20is%20hit%20by%20high%20tariffs%2C%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20sustainability%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20processes%20not%20only%20in%20Godrej%20Agrovet%2C%20but%20in%20all%20Godrej%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202010%2C%20we%20launched%20our%20'good%20and%20green'%20programme%20for%20environmental%20sustainability%20as%20well%20as%20social%20sustainability%2C%20and%20it%20was%20working%20out%20very%20well.%20Subsequently%2C%20we%20had%20compulsory%20CSR%20%5Bcorporate%20social%20responsibility%5D%20spends%2C%20and%20we%20used%20those%20to%20help%20society%20at%20large%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reach%20our%20sustainable%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Godrej%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-day%20meeting%20at%20Davos%20that%20began%20today%20is%20exploring%20how%20to%20relaunch%20growth%2C%20harness%20new%20technologies%20and%20strengthen%20social%20and%20economic%20resilience%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum.%20The%20global%20meeting%20is%20seeing%20participation%20by%20nearly%203%2C000%20leaders%20from%20over%20130%20countries%2C%20including%20350%20governmental%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20participation%20at%20Davos%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20partnerships%2C%20attract%20investment%2C%20and%20position%20the%20country%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20sustainable%20development%20and%20technological%20innovation.%20India%20sent%20five%20Union%20ministers%2C%20three%20chief%20ministers%2C%20and%20ministers%20from%20several%20other%20states%20to%20the%20WEF%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737382980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F6spt1qmg_nadir-godrej_625x300_20_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-davos-2025-godrej-agrovet-chief-nadir-godrej-explains-artificial-intelligence-critical-role-in-food-sector-7518443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20big%20themes%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20has%20been%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20food%20and%20agriculture%20is%20something%20that's%20absolutely%20critical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-davos-2025-godrej-agrovet-chief-nadir-godrej-explains-artificial-intelligence-critical-role-in-food-sector-7518443%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20withdraws%20US%20from%20Paris%20climate%20agreement%20in%20blitz%20of%20executive%20orders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737382440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-the-star-spangled-banner_6805520.jpg%3F20250120180322%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trump-inauguration-trump-to-declare-national-emergency-at-us-mexico-border-in-blitz-of-